Each microserice must have its own database
Welcome Duplication of Data.
We cannot provide ACID Princples to distributed Systems microservices.

1. Database per service Pattern
2. API Composition Pattern:
   When Invoking the Query by invoking serveral Microservices, we will follow API Composition, Gateway Aggreation patterns for combinig the result.
3. CQRS Pattern
4. Event Sourcing Pattern
5. SAGA Pattern